author: dims
msg: - Add licenses for jars that were missing
- Remove licenses for jars that we don't ship
- Add scripting mar to the assembly bin/zip
- Add mex mar to assembly bin/zip
- Make sure the external dependency jars in bin/zip are the same as in webapp/war (except jalopy)
- Don't ship activemq/jms spec jar. activemq jar has a log4j.properties that trips up our typical users who *don't* use jms at all.
- geronimo-annotation jar is needed for jaxws to work
- No need for us to ship servlet api jar since we work in a wide variety of containers (implementing different versions of the servlet spec)
